race.description: Racing Queensland Magic Millions Qtis Open Hcp
race.comment: The $1.5 million QTIS Open. YELLOW BRICK (1) resumes here but had been racing in much sterner company when last in work and should find this assignment a touch easier. Tuned up for this with two strong trial wins and the booking of McDonald in the saddle is key. Goes well first-up and should run a big race while fresh. BOOMTOWN BOSS (5) has been very competitive in all three runs this campaign and will be cherry-ripe now fourth-up. Capable of testing his rivals. JOHN RAMBO (8) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and gets the reliable Gollan/Jones combination. One of the leading prospects. READY TO SCHIPP (3) has won three from four over this journey and shouldn't be underestimated. BOSSED UP (9) rounds out the selections.
